telling some of the stories

00:44:11.160 --> 00:44:11.820
that go untold.

00:44:11.820 --> 00:44:14.700
I mean, the reason Go The Fuck
To Sleep was successful is

00:44:14.700 --> 00:44:17.320
because there's a huge culture
of silence about some of the

00:44:17.320 --> 00:44:20.350
more difficult or complicated
aspects of parenting.

00:44:20.350 --> 00:44:23.920
And we felt like we had a huge
cadre of friends who had

00:44:23.920 --> 00:44:27.950
