new generation of fathers

00:44:27.950 --> 00:44:30.200
needed an outlet to kind
of tell their stories.

00:44:30.200 --> 00:44:31.610
So what we do on the show--

00:44:31.610 --> 00:44:35.710
it's a talk show, and we talk
to mothers and fathers.

00:44:35.710 --> 00:44:39.220
Largely, we bring on people
that we enjoy

00:44:39.220 --> 00:44:40.230
and think are brilliant.

00:44:40.230 --> 00:44:44.800
We bring on a lot of artists,
musicians, writers, and the

00:44:44.800 --> 00:44:47.070
