with their work.

00:44:51.920 --> 00:44:55.030
But the common denominator is
parenthood, and a desire to

00:44:55.030 --> 00:44:58.960
kind of plumb its mysteries
a little deeper.

00:44:58.960 --> 00:45:00.130
So we've been on the
air about a year.

00:45:00.130 --> 00:45:05.210
It's 11:00 to 12:00 Saturdays
on KPFN, and also

00:45:05.210 --> 00:45:05.960
streaming on the web.

