So they just let me
tell it however.

00:47:39.610 --> 00:47:40.810
They didn't impose an ending.

00:47:40.810 --> 00:47:44.400
They didn't say make it happy,
make it tragic and then happy,

00:47:44.400 --> 00:47:45.770
which you do hear a lot.

00:47:45.770 --> 00:47:47.470
So it was great.

00:47:47.470 --> 00:47:49.040
